Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.00,0:00:10.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I'm a soldier  而那也就是说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.27,0:00:13.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是被告也是法官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.54,0:00:19.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我同时站在火线的两端
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:20.14,0:00:26.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,绕过危险的转角  追过生与死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:26.62,0:00:32.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我奔向前挑战谎言的影子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:32.55,0:00:39.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,无论编织出多少谎言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:39.23,0:00:47.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真相还是会照出光明的轮廓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:47.20,0:00:48.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,留着你的眼泪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.77,0:00:50.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,给那一天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:50.31,0:00:53.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,当我们的痛苦都抛在脑后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:53.64,0:00:55.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,站起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:55.28,0:00:56.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟着我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:56.91,0:01:00.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们是士兵不是站着就是死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:00.35,0:01:01.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,留着你的眼泪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:01.88,0:01:03.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,占好你的位置
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:03.49,0:01:06.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把它们留给审判之日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.82,0:01:08.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快速而且自由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:08.42,0:01:09.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟着我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:10.06,0:01:14.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,牺牲的时候到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:14.73,0:01:19.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们只能奋起或是倒地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:19.13,0:01:20.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,攻壳机动队 S.A.C 2nd GIG
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.73,0:02:21.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这里是九州电波塔上空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.90,0:02:25.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,5天前在地下铁工地现场发现的未爆弹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.37,0:02:29.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为有人怀疑可能是大战时使用的战术核武器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.27,0:02:31.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以开始发动集体避难计划
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.67,0:02:32.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在自卫军的指挥之下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.01,0:02:35.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,长达半径30公里的范围内
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.21,0:02:39.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,3500万的一般市民好像终于全部撤退完毕了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.91,0:02:44.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虽然有部分人士臆测这次事件\N或许又是难民的恐怖攻击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.92,0:02:47.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过  在政府没有发表具体消息的状况下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.42,0:02:50.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,自卫军封锁福冈部分地区的这种情势
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.69,0:02:54.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,使得街上呈现出如同下达戒严令的模样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.70,0:02:59.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,#22  无人街
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.81,0:03:06.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因处理爆炸物上行封闭中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.15,0:03:14.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,戒严令吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.15,0:03:19.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,政府的对策确实有问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.09,0:03:22.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过  也不必把行政立法司法三权全部委让给军方吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.99,0:03:24.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.36,0:03:28.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,久世搭乘的伪装船确实在出岛外海沉没
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.20,0:03:31.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是并没有确定那上面有钸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.93,0:03:35.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,至于好像为了帮助伪装船逃走\N所发动的大停电恐怖攻击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.87,0:03:39.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也尚未确定是否真的由难民发动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.71,0:03:44.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,国民对难民的怒气鞭策政府
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.55,0:03:47.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,政府则拿来强化排斥难民的基础
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.72,0:03:50.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没有人肯用自己的脑袋想想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.75,0:03:53.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这个结果意味着什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.22,0:03:57.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算这些都是内厅情报操作的结果
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.79,0:04:00.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已经散布出去的谣言是无法收回来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.73,0:04:02.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,巴特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.13,0:04:05.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,少校怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.40,0:04:08.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在出岛潜入久世的电子脑之后就有点奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.80,0:04:10.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的报告书里面不是有写吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.74,0:04:13.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在集中精力处理核弹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.68,0:04:18.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,内厅已经用报导管制的名目出面去控制现场了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.78,0:04:20.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我去跟总理交涉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.08,0:04:23.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请示能否下定决心对内厅展开搜索
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.49,0:04:26.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就靠这些间接证据吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.26,0:04:34.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在本事件中总理不是也在烦恼\N自卫军进攻出岛这个大问题吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.36,0:04:36.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在这种时期
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.26,0:04:39.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,面对可能变成国家丑闻的案件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.13,0:04:41.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不认为总理会点头同意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.74,0:04:44.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果一个弄得不好  惨遭流弹波及的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.81,0:04:47.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可能又是9课喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.11,0:04:51.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因此我已经安排好让你们可以介入现场
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.88,0:04:53.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去那里挖点东西出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.92,0:04:59.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,少校  我问你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.42,0:05:03.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你认为事到如今难民为什么不开口呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.06,0:05:07.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真相已经在现象面前沉默
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.80,0:05:09.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,久世大概是这么判断的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.50,0:05:14.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在还是保持沉默  甚至对难民也隐瞒真相
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.84,0:05:18.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在某处寻找再度扭转局势的机会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.67,0:05:19.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为什么这么想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.84,0:05:22.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为我如果是他也会这么做的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.12,0:05:30.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,感觉上你的心好像不在这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.55,0:05:32.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们几个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.05,0:05:36.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,确实是被你的才能吸引才会来到这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.16,0:05:40.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过  并没有依赖到连当你的后盾都办不到喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.70,0:05:44.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,谢谢你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.27,0:05:47.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你这种说法我并不讨厌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.94,0:05:51.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,波玛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.07,0:05:54.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你按照预定计划跟帕兹一起\N参加炸弹处理作业
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.84,0:05:56.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,斋藤跟我来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.88,0:05:58.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂  这是干什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.25,0:06:00.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是所有人一起过去吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.68,0:06:02.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我有一个想法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.32,0:06:06.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且我想请你代替我去做某件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.76,0:06:13.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,“日本的奇迹”的准备工作呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.03,0:06:14.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,打扰了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.96,0:06:16.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像已经完成了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.56,0:06:17.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.80,0:06:21.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,演变成令人遗憾的结果
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.34,0:06:25.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,炸弹的拆除作业完成后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.31,0:06:29.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们将召开记者会对国民发表事实真相
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.88,0:06:34.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,接下来大概会演变到\N准许自卫军进攻出岛吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.48,0:06:35.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,总理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.42,0:06:37.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,正如报告书中提到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.35,0:06:41.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,钸交到难民手上的可能性极低
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.86,0:06:45.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,让事情恶化到这个程度的多半就是内厅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.19,0:06:50.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在希望您协助暂缓进攻出岛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.33,0:06:52.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那份报告书我看过了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.34,0:06:56.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是已经超过时限
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.50,0:06:59.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,政府根据俄国当局给的情报
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.81,0:07:03.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,认定钸已经运进出岛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.41,0:07:05.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,并以这一点为决策方针
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.28,0:07:07.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请原谅我插一句话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.82,0:07:10.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这不正是内厅的意图吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.95,0:07:12.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明明没有人希望这么做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.69,0:07:15.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是等在自卫军进攻前方的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.32,0:07:17.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是跟难民间的战争
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.76,0:07:21.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,无论如何  请在内阁会议\N重新讨论报告书的内容
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.36,0:07:25.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果能更早一点看到这个…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.27,0:07:31.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对我来说  公安9课也是最后一张牌了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.44,0:07:40.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,荒卷课长  暂时先这样待命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.38,0:07:42.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.10,0:07:56.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,6班  13班联络本部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.30,0:07:58.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最上层已经部署完毕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.00,0:08:01.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们是公安9课
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.37,0:08:04.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,总理命令我们过来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.41,0:08:06.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我没听过这件事喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.77,0:08:07.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不必在意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.91,0:08:10.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是在事件现场常有的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.11,0:08:12.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.35,0:08:15.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这里有总理的签名
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.78,0:08:18.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要安排这边的技术人员到第一线就可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.79,0:08:20.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没办法  带他们过去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.62,0:08:21.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.79,0:08:27.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那么  你想干什么呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.86,0:08:30.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我找那个西装组人员有点事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.03,0:08:33.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么事呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.43,0:08:36.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,托你的福让我们几乎要关门大吉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.80,0:08:39.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过有两三件事无论如何想要请教
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.61,0:08:41.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.55,0:08:52.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是那个吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.32,0:08:55.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,花五天时间分析构造之后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.19,0:08:58.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在终于要进行拆除作业
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.23,0:09:00.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是公安9课的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.70,0:09:03.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有什么能交给他们的事情请尽量指派
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.77,0:09:07.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,To 茅葺 With Love
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.90,0:09:09.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真低级的情书
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.04,0:09:12.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以前胖子（1945年美国扔在长崎的原子弹）\N和飞毛腿（俄制导弹）的弹头上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.67,0:09:15.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,听说也被写上类似的讯息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.31,0:09:17.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是要模仿美国吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.11,0:09:19.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不知道  到底是为什么呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.85,0:09:22.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,盖格计数器的数值如何
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.85,0:09:23.16,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,盖革计数器：Geiger Counter 用于观察和测量射线密度的仪器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.78,0:09:23.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没有错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.99,0:09:27.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过  他们好像没有技术和时间\N把钸做成核弹头
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.56,0:09:29.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也就是说这只是普通的钸炸弹吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.82,0:09:30.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.96,0:09:35.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是爆炸的话  30公里范围内都会被放射能污染
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.23,0:09:38.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在市民的避难以及日本的奇迹准备完成前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.93,0:09:40.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只能先冷冻炸弹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.94,0:09:42.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没有定时装置吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.80,0:09:44.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幸好没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.27,0:09:45.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原来如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.41,0:09:46.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.27,0:09:49.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这至少安装了振动式压力感应器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.48,0:09:53.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以及光电导装置组成的双重引爆装置
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.78,0:09:57.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等一下  后盖上有东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.65,0:10:00.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你真的是公安吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.66,0:10:02.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大战的时候待过军队
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.56,0:10:06.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,当时我的专长就是设陷阱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.67,0:10:17.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在核弹头拆解处理作业的\N正上方谈天也不坏  对吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.98,0:10:23.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那么  请问你到底打算做到什么程度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.88,0:10:25.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么做到什么程度呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.38,0:10:27.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,状况的恶化啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.95,0:10:32.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这种问题应该去问难民或军事记者吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.49,0:10:34.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那不是我的专业范围
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.89,0:10:36.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是这样吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.46,0:10:40.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,创造用来产生模仿者的媒介者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.10,0:10:44.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这可是你以前研究的分野啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.30,0:10:49.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原本这个社会就蕴含着容易导致这种事态的要素
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.14,0:10:51.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为人类的历史
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.37,0:10:56.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是由编写神话和传说的权力者们创造出来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.78,0:10:59.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在这样的世界上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.45,0:11:01.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不为人知
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.08,0:11:05.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只是不断膨胀自我表现欲望的夸大妄想狂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.09,0:11:08.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想要制造比自己还要高大的英雄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.72,0:11:13.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,个别的11人不就是\N这种犯罪者所制造出来的一种
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.13,0:11:16.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,似是而非的Stand Alone Complex吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.30,0:11:17.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.60,0:11:19.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是令人感兴趣的话题呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.93,0:11:22.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哼  狡猾的家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.74,0:11:25.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但你再怎么说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.27,0:11:27.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还是二流的家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.25,0:11:34.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,关灯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.92,0:11:39.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,盖子没有松掉吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.25,0:11:40.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,安全
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.19,0:11:43.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有了  平行反射型开关一个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.52,0:11:45.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好  放反射镜进去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.50,0:11:51.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,光电导装置全部切断了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.53,0:11:55.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爆缩型核弹的模型
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.53,0:11:55.66,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以239Pu为原料的内爆式核弹临界质量小\N投放在长崎的Fatman就是MK3内爆式核弹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.74,0:12:00.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这表示他们不是没有技术或时间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.27,0:12:03.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只是不做而已吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.05,0:12:14.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是怎么回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.36,0:12:18.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,刚刚有另一个回收班通过这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.36,0:12:19.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你说什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.87,0:12:27.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,波玛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.10,0:12:31.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看了炸弹的构造后有什么印象
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.71,0:12:34.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虽然安排了来自难民的讯息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.01,0:12:35.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过  还是有奇怪的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.04,0:12:36.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.11,0:12:41.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所用的炸弹是美军的M112
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.11,0:12:41.31,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,M112：美军工兵用的塑性炸药\N是将C4密封在墨绿色乙烯树脂袋里并在袋侧附有白色黏着条\N金属探知器对其无效
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.38,0:12:44.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是难民以往使用的C4塑胶炸弹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.75,0:12:45.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.69,0:12:48.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你们在那里留到最后跟移送班会合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.76,0:12:51.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是还没找到本案可能跟内厅有关联的物证
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.63,0:12:53.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在这样就够了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.89,0:12:54.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,了解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.07,0:13:01.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,说我是二流…  这句话是什么意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.64,0:13:07.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们以前遇过Stand Alone型的天才黑客
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.91,0:13:14.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以难免会把他引发的现象跟这次事件比较
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.68,0:13:17.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟他一比较
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.12,0:13:21.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就不会认为在这里自杀的那群人\N有什么了不起的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.66,0:13:26.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以我们调查了个别的11人的外部记忆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.56,0:13:31.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,得知他们只不过是因为病毒而出现的模仿者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.63,0:13:35.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们恐怕是某处的犯罪者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.77,0:13:41.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,巧妙地继承占领中国大使馆的\N那群恐怖份子之名
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.98,0:13:44.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所做出来的思想诱导装置
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.08,0:13:47.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过  那个到处散布病毒的家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.38,0:13:51.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大概认为自己是个优秀的黑客吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.99,0:13:56.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是不是想说那个病毒是我做的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.39,0:13:57.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我没这么说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.03,0:14:02.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那么  你要我说什么呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.93,0:14:06.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是怎么看那群人的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.60,0:14:11.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.84,0:14:12.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那我就来谈谈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.84,0:14:14.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果正如你所说个别的11人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.48,0:14:18.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是因为病毒而出现的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.41,0:14:22.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就跟你说的什么Stand Alone型黑客一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.45,0:14:26.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,仍然继续让状况扩大的他们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.69,0:14:29.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,难道不能说是天才\N不  不能说是英雄吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.56,0:14:34.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们确实通过集体自杀这种表演\N让他们的意思传播出去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.56,0:14:37.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是他们成了谁的英雄？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.23,0:14:38.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,国民的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.90,0:14:40.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,根本不是这么回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.73,0:14:45.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们充其量不过是创造契机\N扩大难民问题的小丑罢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.74,0:14:49.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在他们的死已经被遗忘了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.74,0:14:50.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原来如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.28,0:14:54.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是假设事件的本质不是制造对他们的记忆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.58,0:14:58.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而是制造出目前状况的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.42,0:15:05.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那么  制造“个别的11人”的犯人\N难道不能说是天才黑客吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.29,0:15:08.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很遗憾我无法否认这一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.03,0:15:11.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过即使如此  要是问我犯人是不是天才
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.30,0:15:14.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我还是有一点点存疑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.30,0:15:17.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,从他们的思想和病毒所描绘出的犯人形象
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.91,0:15:21.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只是一个被想要脱离本身自卑感这个欲望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.88,0:15:23.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所支配的个别主义者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.38,0:15:27.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,强迫别人接受自己个人的思想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.05,0:15:29.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,终究无法打动人心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.35,0:15:32.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不管思想里面是善意还是恶意都没关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.75,0:15:35.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要没有某种像是坚定信念的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.96,0:15:38.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就不可能被称为天才或英雄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.59,0:15:41.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,信念？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.13,0:15:42.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.10,0:15:44.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,至少我是这么想的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.47,0:15:45.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然后还有另外一个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.97,0:15:49.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,绝对必要的最大要素
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.34,0:15:51.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,“运”这种东西也是不可或缺的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.11,0:15:53.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.17,0:15:54.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是为什么呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.04,0:15:56.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还用问吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.71,0:15:59.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,天才或英雄这种东西的存在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.68,0:16:02.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,简而言之  绝大部分来自第三者的主观
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.35,0:16:08.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为了让英雄有英雄的样子  首先需要旁观者的反应
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.82,0:16:10.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且这些反应的内容
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.99,0:16:14.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以将英雄捧得高高的  也可以将英雄摔到地上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.46,0:16:16.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这方面只能靠运气了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.93,0:16:21.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原来如此  很有趣的假设
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.17,0:16:25.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过  话说回来\N我不知道你这么健谈啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.71,0:16:27.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这算是赞美吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.78,0:16:30.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你要这么解释也可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.65,0:16:35.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,既然被你赞美  我就顺便再说一个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.28,0:16:39.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,关于这次事件里面的不确定要素
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.34,0:16:56.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在上面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.44,0:17:02.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那一天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.28,0:17:07.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,个别的11人当中唯一没有自杀的久世英雄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.65,0:17:11.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那家伙在那之后不知跑去哪里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.29,0:17:15.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等他再度出现的时候  已经变成难民的指导者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.89,0:17:17.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是奇怪的故事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.93,0:17:19.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这家伙是个偶然吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.96,0:17:22.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还是一开始就计划好的事情呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.67,0:17:28.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为他跟其他11个人做出刚好相反的行动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.97,0:17:31.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,应该是不确定要素吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.87,0:17:37.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过  从结果来看\N他还是对排斥难民有所贡献
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.35,0:17:40.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,行动的种类虽然不同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.75,0:17:45.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但考量最后还是将事态牵引到同一个结论
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.29,0:17:52.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,应该说犯人很漂亮地\N连不确定要素都制造出来不是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.09,0:17:53.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还可以这样掰啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.39,0:17:58.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过  无可讳言那家伙的行动\N确实加速了排斥难民的行为
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.87,0:18:01.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,全国网络上流传的伪装船脱逃剧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.80,0:18:05.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为长崎大停电恐怖攻击\N使得大家留下更深的印象
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.57,0:18:09.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还有现在装在我们正下方的核炸弹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.84,0:18:14.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被久世搞到这样  政府也不得不认真起来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.48,0:18:19.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过  这真的是久世做的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.85,0:18:24.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,难道不是制造久世的犯人捏造出来的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.49,0:18:27.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,更进一步说那个制造一切的犯人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.63,0:18:28.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,难道不能说在不知不觉之间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.93,0:18:34.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已经开始帮助久世\N并且模仿他的行动了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.57,0:18:35.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你这是什么意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.77,0:18:41.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,久世虽然从择捉回来  可是他手上没有钸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.38,0:18:44.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,本来应该要告知难民
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.88,0:18:47.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,暂时先收拾局面才对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.22,0:18:51.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没想到却发生了使用钸元素的恐怖攻击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.49,0:18:52.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那么该怎么办呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.49,0:18:56.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要跟随想要制造自己之人的想法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.59,0:18:58.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虚张声势发出宣战布告吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.63,0:19:01.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过  他什么都没做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.36,0:19:04.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在不但自己闭上嘴  还让难民保持沉默
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.70,0:19:07.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,寻找可以逆转局势的机会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.94,0:19:13.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不  应该说利用保持沉默\N得到能掌控状况的王牌之人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.07,0:19:15.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,反而是久世那一边不是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.21,0:19:19.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果原本只是不确定要素的久世
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.31,0:19:23.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,事实上是真正的天才  英雄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.15,0:19:26.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,难道不能认为总有一天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.19,0:19:29.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以为自己在制造的那一边将会不知不觉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.62,0:19:30.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,变成久世的模仿者吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.16,0:20:04.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,接下来麻烦你们了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.26,0:20:05.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,了解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.33,0:20:15.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们相信捏造的思想而自杀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.34,0:20:17.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,却无法成为任何人的英雄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.10,0:20:21.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们的灵魂现在在哪里徘徊呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.13,0:20:41.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,少校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.40,0:20:44.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,钸的回收顺利吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.93,0:20:46.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,完成了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.57,0:20:47.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.94,0:20:49.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,靠着少校的外部记忆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.90,0:20:52.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我用我的方式谈了久世的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.61,0:20:53.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像还挺顺利的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.61,0:20:56.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.54,0:20:59.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们将直接到Spring 8去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.21,0:21:05.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,情报战的专家太坚持真实性\N反而留下实物成为失败的原因
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.89,0:21:10.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这些钸如果跟从新宿核电厂回收的东西一致
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.22,0:21:13.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就能证明这件事是内厅做的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.79,0:21:14.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,了解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.76,0:21:18.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,合田
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.80,0:21:22.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们也跟久世一样不会轻易放弃的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:22.87,0:21:24.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:29.51,0:21:30.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有一件事忘了问
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.81,0:21:34.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虽然我们认为不会再发作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:34.11,0:21:37.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过  还是搞不清楚病毒的最后一个发作因子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.78,0:21:40.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为了以防万一  还是想预先做好疫苗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:40.35,0:21:42.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果是你的话  会用什么当最后一个因子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:45.29,0:21:48.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果我是犯人的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:50.66,0:21:52.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我大概会放入
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:53.17,0:21:56.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,“义体化前还是处男”这个因子吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.94,0:21:58.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:59.41,0:22:03.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,既然要求为了民众的英雄有殉教的觉悟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:03.51,0:22:05.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就是不可或缺的要素
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:06.31,0:22:10.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其实会出现几个这样的人才\N原本就是一个赌注呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:11.29,0:22:12.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你这家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:12.49,0:22:15.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人再恶劣也要有个限度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:15.12,0:22:16.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:16.89,0:22:19.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不瞒你说  我也是处男呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:21.33,0:22:23.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟你谈话很愉快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:23.56,0:22:24.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不  应该说非常有参考价值
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:24.93,0:22:26.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很感谢你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:27.13,0:22:30.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的战斗也还没有结束
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:30.10,0:22:32.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,究竟是你们先阻止我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:32.91,0:22:35.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还是我的想法先达成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:35.88,0:22:40.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,接下来应该是那个不确定要素掌握关键吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:40.55,0:22:41.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,告辞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:08.61,0:23:15.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,找出我体内行星和星星的银河
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:15.32,0:23:21.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,听着它们每一个都唱着同样宁静的旋律
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:21.86,0:23:25.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我在现实当中从来没看过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:25.83,0:23:28.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样的美丽事物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:29.03,0:23:33.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没有一点怀疑或恐惧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:33.67,0:23:37.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我听到一个声音\N醒来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:37.80,0:23:40.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,听到一个声音呼唤我的名字\N然后现出光明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:40.34,0:23:44.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我省视自身\N醒来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:44.51,0:23:47.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看到一道光随时都围绕着我\N时间已经到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:47.61,0:23:51.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所有真相  所有我需要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:51.12,0:23:56.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去让这一切成真的\N它就在里面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:56.09,0:24:00.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在躯壳里的美丽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:00.33,0:24:04.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我听到一个声音\N醒来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:04.36,0:24:06.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,听到一个声音呼唤我的名字\N然后现出光明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:07.00,0:24:10.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我省视自身\N醒来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:11.04,0:24:14.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看到一道光随时都围绕着我\N时间已经到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:14.31,0:24:17.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所有真相  所有我需要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:17.68,0:24:22.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去让这一切成真的\N它就在里面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:22.68,0:24:27.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就在这个躯壳里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.16,0:00:00.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,
